  "title": "Adhoc Relief Centre Care Taker",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an <strong>Adhoc center care taker</strong> for PlayFACTO School at Tampines Central, Bedok Reservoir and Serangoon Central.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the premise</li>\n  <li>Prepare snacks and warm meals (no cooking required)</li>\n  <li>Provide basic care for students</li>\n  <li>Any ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Working hours are Mon-Fri, 1pm-5pm. Hourly rate of $10. Singaporeans and Singapore PRs only.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested personnel, send your resume by applying for this role or WhatsApp to 81128546.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We seek your understanding that only shortlisted candidates would be contacted.</p>",
